"\n"
"Здравствуйте! Добро пожаловать в Zulip! 👋 "
"{inform_about_tracked_onboarding_messages_text}\n"
"\n"
"{getting_started_text} {organization_setup_text}\n"
"\n"
"{navigation_tour_video_text}\n"
"\n"
"{demo_organization_text}\n"
